<!--miniprogram/pages/detail/detail.wxml-->
<view class="goodsDetail">
  <swiper class="swiper" indicator-dots="{{indicatorDots}}"
  autoplay="{{autoplay}}" interval="{{interval}}" circular="{{circular}}" indicator-color="rgba(255,255,255,0.5)">
    <block wx:for="{{imgUrls}}">
      <swiper-item>
        <image src="{{item}}" class="slide-image" mode="aspectFill"/>
      </swiper-item>
    </block>
  </swiper>
  <view class="header">
    <view class="header-tit"><image src="../../images/tmall.png"></image>iPhoneX钢化膜</view>
    <view class="header-con">
      <text class="now-price">券后<text class="bold">¥5.9</text></text>
      <text class="price">15.9</text>
      <text class="sold">24828件已售</text>
    </view>
    <view class="discount">
      <view class="discount-l">
        <text class="discount-tit">优惠券<text>¥10</text></text>
        <text class="discount-date">使用期限：2019.09.04-2019.09.07</text>
        <image class="discount-gift" src="../../images/gift.png"></image>
      </view>
      <view class="discount-r">
        <button class="receive-btn">立即领取</button>
      </view>
    </view>
  </view>
  <view class="desc">
    <view class="desc-tip">推荐理由</view>
    <view class="desc-con">
      毛绒材质，摸着炒鸡舒服，炒鸡可爱的小鸭子造型，姑娘们最爱的公仔包包~出门拍照必备神器，装点小东西，又方便又可爱~
    </view>
  </view>
</view>